• Trichromatic color theory
Choose 3 primary colors P1, P2, P3. Other colors are deseribed as liners combinations of primary colors. 3 weignts are 3 'coordinates' of color.
Trichromatic theory states that all visible colors may be obtained as combination of 3 primary colors, it was studied in color matching experiments.

